{
  "stem": "27390.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But then, later on, I think it was in the beginning of 1939, they signed the pact with Russia and things deteriorated again.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We lost-- we realized that war is unavoidable.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's-- it's going to happen but what could we do?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't go anywhere.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- some people, if they were very wealthy, managed to get out, but most people couldn't.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Even if they wanted to leave, they couldn't.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was-- also, nobody-- nobody allowed the Jews in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, even if you managed to get over the border somewhere, they wouldn't let you in.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They sent you back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were trapped.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You mean-- yes, we were about maybe a few hundred people, cousins and uncles and don't forget this-- the Jews lived in Poland for a thousand years, over a thousand years and you had relations all over the place, not necessarily in Lodz but whenever there was a wedding, they used to come.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had a lot of people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Usually the weddings were very big.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We used to-- to celebrate all night to the [INAUDIBLE] house and by the time we came out-- I remember once one of my aunts got married and all the relations descended on us.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had about 40 people sleeping in-- in our small apartment on the floor because one didn't have the money and it was unheard of to go and stay in a hotel like today.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If people came, you just put them up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was taken for granted.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You gave them to eat and you gave them where to sleep.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So that's how it was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not before the war.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Some of them left for Russia in the beginning of the war.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, I'm coming to that.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
